+/*
+ * LTT ascii binary buffer to ascii converter.
+ *
+ * Copyright       2008 - 2009   Lai Jiangshan (laijs@cn.fujitsu.com)
+ * Copyright       2009 -        Mathieu Desnoyers mathieu.desnoyers@polymtl.ca
